===Etymology===
Originally written [[𠂇]]. {{liushu|p}} - a left hand. Compare [[又]] ("right hand").

左 was originally a combined form of [[𠂇]] and [[工]] ("work") meaning "to help". But later [[佐]] took this meaning and 左 then took the meaning of [[𠂇]].

